	<h4><span style="color: #0c5c92;">Introduction</span></h4>
<h5><span style="font-weight: normal;">
The </span><span>PM Extras</span><span style="font-weight: normal;"> are a range of more advanced texts designed to provide reading variety to students who have mastered basic literacy skills from the lower level </span><span>PM </span><span style="font-weight: normal;">range and have become fluent readers. Each title has been written, edited, illustrated and carefully levelled so students can enjoy reading success as they are introduced to new characters, concepts, ways of presenting text and a range of genres.&nbsp;<br />
</span></h5>
